extendedInfo.description: Be aware of changes in the economy with this finance tool for managing your portfolio that displays graphs and tables of data for these important economic indicators from the last ten years: Unemployment, GDP, New Home Sales, Orders for Durable Goods and Net Exports . With Internet access, you can also get stock quotes.

reviews.comment: I really like this app. It\'s amazing to see these trends.
